<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-kicker">About Today OS</view>
    <view class="hero-title">关于《今天干点啥》</view>
    <view class="hero-copy">
      这不是单纯的随机推荐器，也不是只会聊天的情侣小工具。它想做的是，把“今天要做什么”变成一条能被发起、被回应、被完成、被记住的生活链路。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">当前版本</view>
    <view class="card">
      <view class="row">
        <view class="label">版本号</view>
        <view class="value">{{version}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="row no-border">
        <view class="label">定位</view>
        <view class="value value-multi">日常生活灵感 + 关系协作小程序</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">已经接上的模块</view>
    <view class="card">
      <view class="module-chip" wx:for="{{modules}}" wx:key="index">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">接下来会继续做什么</view>
    <view class="card">
      <view class="paragraph">1. 继续把通知链路和订阅消息接完整。</view>
      <view class="paragraph">2. 把关系动作沉淀成更完整的回忆页和报告页。</view>
      <view class="paragraph">3. 继续补齐更多本地生活服务与推荐闭环。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">继续逛逛</view>
    <view class="action-list">
      <button class="ghost-button" bindtap="goToHome">去首页</button>
      <button class="ghost-button" bindtap="goToRelation">去关系空间</button>
      <button class="ghost-button" bindtap="goToDiscover">去发现页</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
